                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <desc>
                    The spine strap was added after the binding of the book was completed. Slots were cut in the parchment in order to be able to slide the strap around the binding
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <locus target="#ir(ecto) #iv(erso) #iiiv(erso) #ivr(ecto) #ivv(erso) #94r #94v #95r #95v" facs="001 003 097 098 098 099">Fols. ir(ecto), iv(erso), iiiv(erso), ivr(ecto), ivv(erso), 94r, 94v, 95r, 95v</locus>
